            ],
            "description":"24 skins of some of the most notable characters in the Sonic universe! Replaces the Biome Settlers Pack 2 skin pack. (Note: Amy, Eggman, and Omega are messed up. Feel free to fix them if you can)",
            "license":"unknown",
            "releasenotes": "It is finally finished! Here is my Sonic skin pack, featuring:\n- Sonic The Hedgehog\n- Miles 'Tails' Prower\n- Knuckles The Echidna\n- Shadow The Hedgehog\n- Amy Rose\n- Big The Cat\n- Rouge The Bat\n- E-123 Omega\n- Silver The Hedgehog\n- Blaze The Cat\n- Vector The Crocodile\n- Espio The Chameleon\n- Charmy Bee\n- Jet The Hawk\n- Storm The Albatross\n- Wave The Swallow\n- Sticks The Badger\n- Metal Sonic\n- Cream The Rabbit\n- Dr. Ivo 'Eggman' Robotnik\n- Mighty The Armadillo\n- Ray The Flying Squirrel\n- Princess Sally Acorn\n- Hard Boiled Heavy\n(Note: Amy, Eggman, and Omega are messed up. Feel free to fix them if you can)\n\nAlso, Sticks, and Hard Boiled Heavy were requests by some of my Discord friends. The rest I decided on my own.",
